What is a Russian Manicure?
Before diving into the best places to get your nails done, let's clarify what makes a Russian manicure unique. Originating from Russia, this technique focuses on precise cuticle work using an electric file. This meticulous process results in a cleaner, more refined look that lasts longer than traditional manicures. Paired with intricate Nail Art In Duba  it’s the perfect choice for those seeking flawless, long-lasting nails.

